  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/PackageDescription\/SupportedPlatform\/MacOSVersion\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T13:49:50Z\n---\n\n# SupportedPlatform.MacOSVersion\n\n**Structure**\n\nThe supported macOS version.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstruct MacOSVersion\n```\n\n## Type Properties\n\n- **v10_10**: The value that represents macOS 10.10.\n- **v10_11**: The value that represents macOS 10.11.\n- **v10_12**: The value that represents macOS 10.12.\n- **v10_13**: The value that represents macOS 10.13.\n- **v10_14**: The value that represents macOS 10.14.\n- **v10_15**: The value that represents macOS 10.15.\n- **v11**: The value that represents macOS 11.0.\n- **v12**: The value that represents macOS 12.0.\n- **v13**: The value that represents macOS 13.0.\n- **v14**: The value that represents macOS 14.0.\n- **v15**: The value that represents macOS 15.0.\n- **v26**: The value that represents macOS 26.0.\n\n## Supporting macOS\n\n- **macOS(_:)**: Configures the minimum deployment target version for the macOS platform.\n- **macOS(_:)**: Configures the minimum deployment target version for the macOS platform using a version string.\n- **macOS**: The macOS platform.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
